    None,
    Array(TypeNameArray),

    Pointer(TypeNamePointer),
    Reference(TypeNameReference),

    Struct(TypeNameStruct),
    Tuple(TypeNameTuple),
    Trait(TypeNameTrait),
    Unit,
}
